Imro Fox https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Imro_Fox 0 Imro Fox (May 21, 1862 – March 4, 1910) was German-born American chef who became a headlining stage magician billed as the "comic conjuror". He was active between 1880 and 1910 and was known for the line, "Mahvelous! Everything I do is mahvelous."
